<paragraph base="F45929601" id="IFRS16_98"><paranum>98</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="98"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0323">If an entity (the seller-<xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref>) transfers an asset to another entity (the buyer-<xref base="F45929747" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0382">lessor<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0222"/></ph></xref>) and leases that asset back from the buyer-lessor, both the seller-lessee and the buyer-lessor shall account for the transfer <xref base="F45929889" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0398">contract<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0049"/></ph></xref> and the <xref base="F47380071" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_DI0011" scope="local">lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0214"/></ph></xref> applying <xref base="F47961173" href="IFRS16_g99-103.dita#IFRS16_g99-103/IFRS16_g99-103_TI" id="IFRS16_X0324">paragraphs 99&#x2013;103</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>